<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>404页面未找到</title>
    <style>
        body { 
            font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, sans-serif; 
            text-align: center; 
            padding: 50px; 
            line-height: 1.6; 
            color: #333;
        }
        .container { 
            max-width: 600px; 
            margin: 0 auto; 
        }
        h1 { 
            font-size: 3em; 
            margin-bottom: 0.2em; 
            color: #555; 
        }
        .error-code { 
            font-size: 8em; 
            font-weight: bold; 
            color: #e0e0e0; 
            margin: 0; 
            line-height: 1;
        }
        .actions { 
            margin: 30px 0; 
        }
        .btn { 
            display: inline-block; 
            margin: 5px; 
            padding: 12px 24px; 
            background: #007bff; 
            color: white; 
            text-decoration: none; 
            border-radius: 4px; 
        }
        .btn:hover { 
            background: #0056b3; 
        }
        .search-box { 
            margin: 20px auto; 
            max-width: 400px; 
        }
        input[type="text"] { 
            width: 70%; 
            padding: 10px; 
            border: 1px solid #ddd; 
            border-radius: 4px 0 0 4px; 
        }
        input[type="submit"] { 
            width: 30%; 
            padding: 10px; 
            background: #28a745; 
            color: white; 
            border: 1px solid #28a745; 
            border-radius: 0 4px 4px 0; 
            cursor: pointer; 
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="error-code">404</div>
        <h1>页面未找到</h1>
        <p>抱歉，您访问的页面已经删除</p>
        <p>请检查您输入的网址是否正确，或尝试以下方法：</p>
        <div class="actions">
            <a href="/" class="btn">返回网站首页</a>
            <a href="javascript:history.back();" class="btn" style="background:#6c757d;">返回上一页</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>